<p align="center">Denude Clothing would like to use cookies to store information on your computer to improve the functionality available to you through this website. Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer by websites that you visit. They are widely used in order to make websites work, or work more efficiently, as well as to provide information to the owners of the site. Denude Clothing, uses cookies to store session information which are removed at the end of the connection.
  
  The purpose of these session cookies is to record what you have put in your basket and to enable you to use the shopping cart and pay online. They are essential to enable the site to operate and without them, you will not be able to place food and drink orders online.
  
  You may delete and block all cookies from this site, but you will not be able to purchase catering for your box online. This website also uses cookies for Google Analytics tracking code. To opt out of being tracked by Google Analytics across all websites, please visit http://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout
  
  Most web browsers allow some control of most cookies through the browser settings. To find out more about cookies, including how to see what cookies have been set and how to manage and delete them, please visit www.allaboutcookies.org/manage-cookies</p>
